Body: UNIQUE SELLING POINTS (USP) https://medium.com/@alphaxblog/unique-selling-points-usp-4f8a5d5170e7  ALPHA-X COIN (AX) The coins, distributed through the main chain in the ICO, are Alpha-X coins. This is a POS based crypto-currency and hence is quite fast, secure and anonymous. We intend to promote it as a Utility Coin, through which we will increase the utility proposition within the market and, at the right time, we can even integrate point-of-sale (POS) into AX.  ALPHA-X EXCHANGE (AXE) This will be created at a later stage using the ICO funds of AX. It will be launched as a global crypto-currency exchange, with the intention of providing more and more liquidity to different Fiat-Crypto pairs. The mission is to get up to 100 plus pairs of Fiat / Crypto-currency and make the exchange accessible to everyone around the globe.  ALPHA-X WALLET A decentralised QT wallet for Windows, Mac and Linux clients for storing, sending, receiving and minting new Alpha-X coin. The user will hold his private keys in here and hence it’s the most secure way to keep your money with you.  ALPHA-X MOBILE APP This is a lightweight interface, where all the related activities will take place. It is where the user can put their coin and can spend it whenever, and wherever, required.  ALPHA-X MARKET An online marketplace, which will to bring the merchants and buyers closer together. Here the participating merchants can sell their merchandise directly to the buyers who will use Alpha-X coins.  ALPHA-X DEBIT CARD Alpha-X inteads to provide true liquidity to its users, around the globe and around the clock. Anyone can buy or sell Alpha-X in their own locality, at any time, without any problem. We intend to provide AX debit cards as well, and integrate them with point of sale.
